by the examination papers.

873
00:37:51,980 --> 00:37:52,860
The new anonymous grading system

874
00:37:52,900 --> 00:37:54,900
has also been implemented
in the recent provincial examinations.

875
00:37:54,980 --> 00:37:55,820
For next year's Imperial Examination,

876
00:37:56,170 --> 00:37:57,980
all examination halls will implement
the new system.

877
00:37:58,340 --> 00:37:59,020
Other than that,

878
00:37:59,100 --> 00:38:00,990
post stations have been set up
in several counties

879
00:38:00,990 --> 00:38:01,740
near the capital

880
00:38:01,870 --> 00:38:03,540
to provide travel vouchers and subsidies

881
00:38:03,660 --> 00:38:04,580
for underprivileged students

882
00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:05,990
heading to the capital for exams.

883
00:38:06,220 --> 00:38:07,430
After implementing this policy,

884
00:38:07,740 --> 00:38:09,100
it has raised the public spirit.

885
00:38:09,510 --> 00:38:11,510
The number of candidates
is increasing daily.

886
00:38:11,740 --> 00:38:12,510
Your Majesty,

887
00:38:12,580 --> 00:38:15,310
it's commendable to give
underprivileged students opportunities.

888
00:38:15,390 --> 00:38:17,790
However, adding new rules
and rejecting pre-submitted work

889
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:19,580
will increase the burden on examiners.

890
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:21,430
I have heard during the recent exams,

891
00:38:21,430 --> 00:38:22,910
there were several cases
of misjudgments,

892
00:38:23,310 --> 00:38:24,580
leading candidates to protest
at the government office.

893
00:38:24,950 --> 00:38:25,790
The capital's post stations

894
00:38:25,830 --> 00:38:27,740
also experienced chaos and overcrowding.

895
00:38:28,310 --> 00:38:30,030
The imperial exams are held
once every three years.

896
00:38:30,310 --> 00:38:31,910
Relying on a single exam
to determine success

897
00:38:32,030 --> 00:38:34,140
can lead to talented individuals
being overlooked

898
00:38:34,140 --> 00:38:36,140
and mediocre ones being selected.

899
00:38:36,430 --> 00:38:38,100
If the chief examiner could understand

900
00:38:38,220 --> 00:38:39,580
some genuinely talented candidates

901
00:38:39,580 --> 00:38:41,260
through pre-submitted work,

902
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:42,660
they would be better informed.

903
00:38:42,790 --> 00:38:43,950
Hastily abolishing this system

904
00:38:44,140 --> 00:38:46,100
could compromise fairness.

905
00:38:46,830 --> 00:38:48,220
Better informed, huh?

906
00:38:48,740 --> 00:38:50,870
Is it better informed
about the candidates' talents

907
00:38:50,870 --> 00:38:53,220
or the candidates' family backgrounds?

908
00:38:54,950 --> 00:38:55,700
Your Majesty,

909
00:38:56,390 --> 00:38:57,260
I believe

910
00:38:57,540 --> 00:38:59,030
