911
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:01,510
can lead to collusion
between candidates and examiners,

912
00:39:01,700 --> 00:39:03,030
abolishing it is the right move.

913
00:39:03,540 --> 00:39:05,540
As for Mr. Li's concerns,

914
00:39:05,910 --> 00:39:09,180
the issue lies not in the new system
but in academic administration.

915
00:39:09,870 --> 00:39:13,510
Appointing competent officials
to enhance academic administration

916
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:16,790
to support the new exams is the way
to address the fundamental problems.

917
00:39:24,470 --> 00:39:25,740
A new system will inevitably

918
00:39:26,100 --> 00:39:27,390
have some shortcomings at first.

919
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:28,950
We can address them one by one.

920
00:39:29,620 --> 00:39:30,660
If we hesitate

921
00:39:30,790 --> 00:39:32,310
and cling to old practices,

922
00:39:32,540 --> 00:39:33,990
then reforms throughout history

923
00:39:34,260 --> 00:39:35,390
would never have succeeded.

924
00:39:35,870 --> 00:39:36,430
Mr. Shen,

925
00:39:37,430 --> 00:39:38,870
you can proceed without hesitation.

926
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:41,470
Thank you, Your Majesty.

927
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:43,580
Speaking of the imperial exams,

928
00:39:44,140 --> 00:39:46,140
let's discuss the central six academies.

929
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:48,540
The annual exams
of the Imperial Academy's six subjects

930
00:39:48,990 --> 00:39:50,700
have produced talents like Zhao Qi,

931
00:39:50,910 --> 00:39:52,030
who is not interested
in becoming an official.

932
00:39:52,430 --> 00:39:53,510
The School of Integrity

933
00:39:53,950 --> 00:39:56,100
initially established
to promote female education,

934
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:58,540
has been overlooked in recent years.

935
00:39:59,030 --> 00:40:00,470
I want you to oversee

936
00:40:00,620 --> 00:40:02,700
this year's exams for both schools.

937
00:40:03,310 --> 00:40:04,790
I want you to keep an eye

938
00:40:05,310 --> 00:40:06,790
on those with genuine talent

939
00:40:07,220 --> 00:40:09,180
and high aspirations for me.

940
00:40:09,830 --> 00:40:11,580
I shall obey, Your Majesty.

941
00:40:14,310 --> 00:40:14,870
Yes, Your Majesty.

942
00:40:18,940 --> 00:40:19,700
[Benefit All Beings]

943
00:40:19,700 --> 00:40:21,030
Trinkets for sale!

944
00:40:21,660 --> 00:40:22,220
Master,

945
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:24,220
we should have that fox Kong sit

946
00:40:24,350 --> 00:40:26,350
on our interrogation bench for a while.

947
00:40:27,180 --> 00:40:28,950
He has been in charge of the bureau
for so many years

948
00:40:29,350 --> 00:40:31,430
because of his clean reputation.

949
00:40:32,620 --> 00:40:33,830
Now, he is still untouchable.

950
00:40:34,060 --> 00:40:36,910
Are we going to watch him guard
while secretly stealing

951
00:40:37,140 --> 00:40:38,510
and let Yang take the fall?

952
00:40:38,830 --> 00:40:40,910
Yang was just a pawn.

953
00:40:43,790 --> 00:40:45,950
Have a taste of our fine wine!

954
00:40:49,620 --> 00:40:50,580
This is the finest tea

955
00:40:52,350 --> 00:40:54,140
of the year.

956
00:40:54,260 --> 00:40:55,990
Mr. Kong, have a cup.

957
00:41:03,830 --> 00:41:05,510
Tea can be refilled once spilled.

958
00:41:06,700 --> 00:41:08,790
But if someone gets a hold
of your weaknesses,

959
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:11,140
it will be hard to break free.

960
00:41:11,580 --> 00:41:12,740
I was careless.

961
00:41:12,990 --> 00:41:13,870
But don't worry.

962
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:16,990
I've cleaned up
the Bureau of Salt and Iron thoroughly.

963
00:41:17,180 --> 00:41:19,060
Xiao Heng won't find anything.

964
00:41:19,950 --> 00:41:21,100
I hope so.

965
00:41:35,430 --> 00:41:36,350
- Father.
- Father.

966
00:41:37,870 --> 00:41:39,950
Do you know why I asked you here?

967
00:41:43,220 --> 00:41:44,870
The money from the bureau
has been cut off

968
00:41:45,310 --> 00:41:47,100
[Li Jing]
and that side needs money.

969
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:50,700
We need to fill this gap.

970
00:41:50,830 --> 00:41:51,830
Where should we start?

971
00:41:52,030 --> 00:41:52,910
- The Ye family.
- The Ye.

972
00:41:53,430 --> 00:41:54,790
The Ye and the Jiang family

973
00:41:55,620 --> 00:41:56,830
are in-laws.

974
00:41:57,180 --> 00:41:58,790
Since Jiang Yuanbai remarried

975
00:41:59,310 --> 00:42:00,740
and Ye Zhenzhen's daughter, Jiang Li,

976
00:42:01,220 --> 00:42:02,470
was sent to the Zhennv Hall,

977
00:42:02,700 --> 00:42:04,540
the Ye and the Jiang families

978
00:42:05,060 --> 00:42:06,790
have not been in contact since.

979
00:42:07,140 --> 00:42:08,220
[Li Lian]
The Ye family may be wealthy.

980
00:42:08,620 --> 00:42:10,060
But they lack prestige.

981
00:42:10,700 --> 00:42:12,740
Two years ago,
the Ye family used various means

982
00:42:12,870 --> 00:42:15,260
to get their son, Ye Shijie,

983
00:42:15,700 --> 00:42:16,740
into the Imperial Academy

984
00:42:16,990 --> 00:42:18,220
to study with us.

985
00:42:18,700 --> 00:42:19,620
If we control him,

986
00:42:20,030 --> 00:42:21,740
won't we control the entire Ye family?

987
00:42:22,030 --> 00:42:23,350
If you've thought of this,

988
00:42:23,830 --> 00:42:24,950
why didn't you take action?

989
00:42:25,310 --> 00:42:26,540
Ye Shijie is arrogant.

990
00:42:27,180 --> 00:42:29,060
We haven't found
the right opportunity yet.

991
00:42:34,870 --> 00:42:36,990
I'll pave the way for you.

992
00:42:38,580 --> 00:42:39,180
- Yes, Father.
- Yes, Father.

993
00:42:52,060 --> 00:42:54,220
Why aren't you drinking, Shen?

994
00:42:56,910 --> 00:42:57,700
A toast to you, Your Highness.

995
00:42:58,580 --> 00:43:01,580
Even your posture while holding
the wine glass looks graceful.

996
00:43:02,430 --> 00:43:03,540
No need for your toast.

997
00:43:04,390 --> 00:43:06,870
Today's banquet is for you.

998
00:43:07,430 --> 00:43:09,540
I heard His Majesty has appointed you

999
00:43:09,700 --> 00:43:11,830
to oversee the examinations
at both schools.

1000
00:43:12,510 --> 00:43:14,510
You're truly a talented individual.

1001
00:43:16,540 --> 00:43:17,350
Thank you, Your Highness.

1002
00:43:26,390 --> 00:43:28,620
These are the schools
where talented individuals enter.

1003
00:43:28,990 --> 00:43:31,660
I'll carefully consider His Majesty's
intentions and work hard.

1004
00:43:32,030 --> 00:43:35,220
If it were just a routine examination,
it wouldn't be interesting.

1005
00:43:35,660 --> 00:43:37,470
How about a joint competition,

1006
00:43:37,740 --> 00:43:39,830
where the young gentlemen
from the Imperial Academy team up

1007
00:43:40,030 --> 00:43:43,470
with the ladies
from the School of Integrity?

1008
00:43:43,660 --> 00:43:44,990
That would be so interesting.

1009
00:43:45,470 --> 00:43:47,140
I'm looking forward to it.

1010
00:43:47,540 --> 00:43:48,260
No, that's not feasible.

1011
00:43:48,540 --> 00:43:49,580
After all, this is the Entry Exam

1012
00:43:49,990 --> 00:43:50,830
and should be taken seriously.

1013
00:43:51,470 --> 00:43:53,830
Why can't we try something innovative?

1014
00:43:54,580 --> 00:43:55,790
If we follow Your Highness's suggestion,

1015
00:43:56,100 --> 00:43:57,870
it may lead
to students forming factions,

1016
00:43:58,140 --> 00:44:00,430
which could harm the integrity
of our officials in the future.

1017
00:44:00,870 --> 00:44:02,620
Those with true talent

1018
00:44:02,870 --> 00:44:03,870
but poor social skills

1019
00:44:04,030 --> 00:44:05,510
or family background

1020
00:44:05,910 --> 00:44:07,510
might be overlooked.

1021
00:44:07,990 --> 00:44:10,700
This would not be beneficial
for our government's integrity.

1022
00:44:15,700 --> 00:44:19,140
You really are a clean young official
without flaws.

1023
00:44:22,510 --> 00:44:23,510
But I don't like it

1024
00:44:23,510 --> 00:44:25,180
when you talk to me so seriously.

1025
00:44:25,830 --> 00:44:26,740
It makes me uncomfortable.

1026
00:44:27,660 --> 00:44:28,220
On your knees.

1027
00:44:28,870 --> 00:44:29,470
Your Highness.

1028
00:44:30,430 --> 00:44:31,140
I said, kneel.

